  • Classes in model used by model 
    Class and Description
    album
    album class is the class that hold all the photos(Reference of photo as imgR) It used an ArrayList to hold all the imgR object

    imgR
    imgR is a reference point of an image.
    tag
    tag class is a attribute that belongs to the image(imgR)
    taglist
    taglist contains a list of tag and imgR can access its tag from the taglist
    user
    user is an object represent the user.
    userlist
    userlist is a list of all the users
